transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello? Hello? Ha, Ajeet bhai.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Pawan baat kar raha tha. Kaise hai sir?
Customer: Ji ji badhiya.
Executive: Ha sir. To mai ye keh raha tha ki yaha pe jo aapke ek inquiry aayi thi unse aapne connect kiya tha?
Customer: Kaun si?
Executive: Ye abhi aaya hua dekho na sir Mumbai se coaster wooden resin tea coaster.
Customer: Resin. Ek minute. Ha.
Executive: Pankti naam hai sir. Wooden resin mein chahiye sir dekho na sir.

Customer: [unintelligible]
Executive: WhatsApp pe call kariye.
Customer: Nahi WhatsApp pe nahi sir. WhatsApp pe nahi hai. 108, 105, 94 abhi tak aa chuka hai. Ye WhatsApp pe nahi hai. Ispe lead manage hota hai sir.
Customer: Ha WhatsApp pe call kariye ek second.
Executive: Achcha WhatsApp pe call karu kya? Achcha achcha. Ek baar Google Meet pe aa jaye kya?
Customer: [unintelligible]
Executive: Achcha theek hai theek hai WhatsApp mai samajh gaya aapka khulega nahi wo. Theek hai theek hai pata chal gaya.
